=head1 NAME

zdkimfilter - DKIM filter for the Courier mail server

=head1 SYNOPSIS

2idn I<punycode-name> ...

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Internationalized Domain Name (IDNA2008) decode punycode names back to
UTF-8, by calling I<idn2_to_unicode_8z8z>.  This is the opposite of
I<idn2>; that is, the same of I<idn2 --decode>, except that the latter
not always exists.

